    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presented in showroom-equivalent condition, this vehicle has been curated by a meticulous enthusiast with an open-checkbook maintenance philosophy. The exterior paint retains its original factory depth and luster, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating; there are absolutely no rock chips, swirl marks, or door dings to be found. The wheels are free of any curb rash and are wrapped in high-performance tires with near-full tread depth. Inside, the cabin is a true time capsule. The premium leather upholstery remains supple with no visible bolster wear, the carpets have been protected by heavy-duty liners since day one, and the interior still carries that distinct new-car aroma. Every electronic component, from the infotainment system to the heated seat elements, functions perfectly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, featuring a fully documented service history with recent fluid flushes and a clean bill of health from a marque specialist. This vehicle has been strictly garage-kept, never driven in inclement weather, and hand-washed only. It comes complete with all original keys, owner\u2019s manuals, and a comprehensive binder of service receipts.",
